.TH SIMREADER 1 "2025-01-01" "simreader 1.0.0" "User Commands"

.SH NAME
simreader \- Unified SIM/USIM card reader tool

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B simreader
[\fIOPTIONS\fR]

.SH DESCRIPTION
simreader is a comprehensive tool for reading and analyzing SIM and USIM cards. It supports both traditional 2G SIM cards and modern 3G/4G/5G USIM cards, providing detailed analysis of card structure and contents.

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-v, \-\-verbose\fR
Show verbose output including APDUs and hex dumps
.TP
\fB\-j, \-\-json\fR
Output in JSON format
.TP
\fB\-e, \-\-explore\fR
Explore all accessible SIM files
.TP
\fB\-a, \-\-analysis\fR
Complete analysis with recommendations
.TP
\fB\-r, \-\-reader\fR \fINAME\fR
Specify reader name
.TP
\fB\-p, \-\-pin\fR
Prompt for PIN (not implemented)
.TP
\fB\-h, \-\-help\fR
Show this help message
.TP
\fB\-\-version\fR
Show version information

.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
\fBsimreader\fR
Basic SIM information
.TP
\fBsimreader -a\fR
Complete analysis with recommendations
.TP
\fBsimreader -e -v\fR
Explore all files with verbose output
.TP
\fBsimreader -j\fR
Output in JSON format

.SH OUTPUT
The tool can extract:
.TP
\- ICCID (SIM serial number)
.TP
\- IMSI (subscriber identity)
.TP
\- SPN (service provider name)
.TP
\- Network information and preferences
.TP
\- SMS service parameters
.TP
\- Emergency call codes
.TP
\- Language preferences

.SH LIMITATIONS
.TP
\- Cannot extract contacts stored in phone memory
.TP
\- Cannot extract contacts stored in cloud services
.TP
\- Cannot extract SMS messages stored in phone memory
.TP
\- Cannot extract call history, photos, videos, or apps

.SH REQUIREMENTS
.TP
\- PC/SC Lite library (pcsclite)
.TP
\- Compatible SIM card reader (ACS ACR38U-CCID supported)
.TP
\- Root or appropriate permissions to access smart card devices

